#### `TrackBalls`

**Input: `TrackingRequest`**

| Field           | Type                | Units | Shape                       | Constraints                     |
| --------------- | ------------------- | ----- | --------------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| `experiment_id` | `string`            | —     | scalar                      | Non-empty, valid UUID v4        |
| `seeds`         | `repeated BallSeed` | —     | [S], S ∈ [1, 3 × N_cameras] | At least 1 seed; ≤ 3 per camera |

**`BallSeed` sub-message**

| Field       | Type      | Units       | Shape  | Constraints                            |
| ----------- | --------- | ----------- | ------ | -------------------------------------- |
| `ball_id`   | `int32`   | —           | scalar | ∈ {0, 1, 2}; consistent across cameras |
| `camera_id` | `int32`   | —           | scalar | ∈ {0, 1}                               |
| `frame_idx` | `int32`   | frame count | scalar | ≥ 0; must exist in frame directory     |
| `x`         | `float32` | pixels      | scalar | [0, frame_width)                       |
| `y`         | `float32` | pixels      | scalar | [0, frame_height)                      |

> **Note on `ball_id`:** The same `ball_id` across different `camera_id` seeds means "this is the same physical ball." Node assigns `ball_id` from the order the user clicks in the UI; 0-indexed.

**Output stream: `TrackingStatus`**

| Field              | Type                    | Units       | Shape   | Constraints                                     |
| ------------------ | ----------------------- | ----------- | ------- | ----------------------------------------------- |
| `frame`            | `int32`                 | frame count | scalar  | ≥ 0; monotonically increasing                   |
| `progress`         | `float32`               | fraction    | scalar  | [0.0, 1.0]                                      |
| `points`           | `repeated TrackedPoint` | —           | [B × C] | One entry per (ball_id, camera_id) pair         |
| `frame_confidence` | `float32`               | —           | scalar  | [0.0, 1.0]; SAM2 mask confidence for this frame |

**`TrackedPoint` sub-message**

| Field        | Type      | Units                | Shape  | Constraints                      |
| ------------ | --------- | -------------------- | ------ | -------------------------------- |
| `ball_id`    | `int32`   | —                    | scalar | ∈ {0, 1, 2}                      |
| `camera_id`  | `int32`   | —                    | scalar | ∈ {0, 1}                         |
| `x`          | `float32` | pixels (undistorted) | scalar | [0, frame_width)                 |
| `y`          | `float32` | pixels (undistorted) | scalar | [0, frame_height)                |
| `confidence` | `float32` | —                    | scalar | [0.0, 1.0]; per-point confidence |

Stream terminates on last frame. Node persists the full point set to `results/tracks.json`.

